header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - 2ND ROUND

videos.description: Tyus Battle fights through traffic to score on a layup while being fouled against Miami.
videos.headline: Battle gets tough layup to fall for Syracuse

videos.description: Miami's Ebuka Izundu gets a block at the rim against Syracuse's Tyler Lydon .
videos.headline: Izundu protects the paint for Miami with powerful block

videos.description: Miami head coach Jim Larranaga discusses his offensive and defense adjustments to make for the 2nd half against Syracuse.
videos.headline: Jim Larranaga on his team's 1st half performance vs Syracuse

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyus Battle knocks down a corner 3 to give Syracuse its first lead of the half over Miami.
videos.headline: Syracuse takes its first lead of the second half

videos.description: Miami's Anthony Lawrence Jr. finds Kamari Murphy for an alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Murphy throws down alley-oop slam in close game

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyus Battle misses on a two-handed slam which leads to dunk from Miami's Kamari Murphy at the other end.
videos.headline: Syracuse missed dunk leads to key Miami hoop

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon knocks down a 3-pointer to cut into Miami's lead.
videos.headline: Syracuse pulls within two in final minute

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon misses a game-tying 3-pointer with under five seconds left on the clock.
videos.headline: Gillon misses game-tying 3-pointer in final seconds

videos.description: Miami's Kamari Murphy discusses his thoughts on Miami's 62-57 victory over Syracuse.
videos.headline: Kamari Murphy on winning close game against Syracuse in front of friends and family
